><description>&lt;p&gt;妈妈，今天哪儿也不去，就在家里玩&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;妈妈，怎么又到这里了?&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;我自己走，不要抱&lt;br&gt; sent with mobile&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-2289533230155284147?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2010/03/blog-post.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-8366382449502493737</guid><pubDate>Thu, 18 Feb 2010 03:40:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2010-02-18T11:40:31.849+08:00</atom:updated><title>小宝最喜欢的语言</title><description>小宝把所有的东西都叫宝宝，从箱子宝宝，到火车宝宝，爸爸宝宝，甚至大便宝宝。。。周围的东西都可以加上宝宝这个后缀。&lt;br&gt; &lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-8366382449502493737?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2010/02/blog-post.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-6434933963593972019</guid><pubDate>Tue, 27 Oct 2009 10:13:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-10-27T18:14:33.755+08:00</atom:updated><title></title><description>&lt;p class="mobile-photo"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/uploaded_images/=?UTF-8?B?5Zu+5YOPMDA0NS5qcGc=?=-773756-773788"&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/uploaded_images/=?UTF-8?B?5Zu+5YOPMDA0NS5qcGc=?=-773756-773784"  border="0" alt="" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-6434933963593972019?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/10/blog-post_27.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-310468154025954914</guid><pubDate>Sun, 11 Oct 2009 01:40:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-10-11T09:40:50.657+08:00</atom:updated><title>小宝唱歌：五星红旗迎风飘扬</title><description>小宝这两天喜欢五星红旗，开始唱：五星红旗迎风飘扬了。&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-310468154025954914?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/10/blog-post_11.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-2923719604670070571</guid><pubDate>Sat, 10 Oct 2009 14:51:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-10-10T22:51:15.423+08:00</atom:updated><title>老宝</title><description>小宝喜欢管妈妈叫：老妈；管爸爸叫：老爸。然后管自己叫：老宝。&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-2923719604670070571?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/10/blog-post_9597.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-4445353551120960658</guid><pubDate>Sat, 10 Oct 2009 14:27:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-10-10T22:27:27.269+08:00</atom:updated><title>小家伙又从床上掉下来了</title><description>小宝晚上从床上掉下来，没什么大问题，就是左边脸蛋儿红红的。&lt;p&gt;这个淘气的小家伙。&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-4445353551120960658?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/10/blog-post_887.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-8329817711730729799</guid><pubDate>Sat, 10 Oct 2009 09:13:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-10-10T17:13:34.469+08:00</atom:updated><title>爸爸打屁股</title><description>小宝两岁四个月了，居然开始调皮得天天故意尿裤子。&lt;p&gt;每次都是一边嘴里喊着：&amp;quot;尿尿！尿尿！&amp;quot;，一边就尿在了裤子上，然后嬉皮笑脸的说：&amp;quot;没憋住！没憋住！&amp;quot;&lt;p&gt;昨天爸爸把小家伙抓到黑屋子里面打屁股。小宝象征性的猛哭了一阵，就高高兴兴的推门出去找妈妈玩去了。&lt;p&gt;今天问小宝：&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;小宝，昨天你犯什么错误了？&amp;quot;&lt;br&gt;&amp;quot;尿裤子了&amp;quot;&lt;br&gt;&amp;quot;尿裤子要怎么样？&amp;quot;&lt;br&gt;&amp;quot;打屁股&amp;quot;&lt;br&gt;&amp;quot;爸爸打屁股疼不疼？&amp;quot;&lt;br&gt;&amp;quot;不。。。。。疼！&amp;quot;&lt;p&gt;嗨。教育失败。&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-8329817711730729799?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/10/blog-post_10.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-8236799583094255517</guid><pubDate>Sat, 03 Oct 2009 11:30:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-10-03T19:30:48.052+08:00</atom:updated><title>爸爸忘记了</title><description>中秋夜，全家在阳台上摆起晚餐，赏月吃月饼。&lt;p&gt;爸爸用四个杯子给爸爸妈妈爷爷奶奶各倒了一杯酒。&lt;p&gt;小宝在旁边急了：&amp;quot;爸爸忘记呢！爸爸忘记呢！&amp;quot;&lt;p&gt;我问小宝：&amp;quot;爸爸忘记什么了？&amp;quot;&lt;p&gt;小宝说：&amp;quot;爸爸忘记。。。拿。。。小宝的。。。酒杯呢！&amp;quot;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-8236799583094255517?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/10/blog-post_03.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-2183128529805725410</guid><pubDate>Thu, 01 Oct 2009 14:16:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-10-01T22:16:05.092+08:00</atom:updated><title>爸爸，出去！</title><description>爸爸推门进卧室：&lt;br&gt;"爸爸。。。 出去！&lt;br&gt;小宝在看弗洛格，你进来干什么？"&lt;br&gt; &lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-2183128529805725410?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/10/blog-post_01.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-9097402961140426002</guid><pubDate>Thu, 01 Oct 2009 10:57:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-10-01T18:57:29.325+08:00</atom:updated><title>小家伙又尿裤子了</title><description>我是一个伏洛格。。。伏洛格的妈妈。。。。伏洛格的爸爸。。。。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;爸爸。。。。 爸爸。。。&lt;br&gt;换个新的裤子，没有尿的。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;唉。。。。&lt;br&gt; &lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-9097402961140426002?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/10/blog-post.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-1097670123973605665</guid><pubDate>Wed, 30 Sep 2009 12:44:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-09-30T20:44:47.511+08:00</atom:updated><title>看这一页</title><description>。这个是什么？&lt;br&gt;是妈妈。&lt;br&gt;。谁的尾巴长？&lt;br&gt;妈妈的尾巴长。&lt;br&gt;。小宝不知道。&lt;br&gt;知道！知道！这是扇子书！&lt;br&gt;猴子尾巴长！&lt;br&gt;这里有个臭妈妈！&lt;p&gt;。睡觉了！&lt;br&gt;Daddy, 快起来！&lt;p&gt;-- &lt;br&gt;Sent from my mobile device&lt;p&gt;Jian Shuo Wang&lt;br&gt;blog: &lt;a href="http://home.wangjianshuo.com"&gt;http://home.wangjianshuo.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;email: &lt;a href="mailto:jianshuo@gmail.com"&gt;jianshuo@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;company: &lt;a href="http://baixing.com"&gt;baixing.com&lt;/a&gt; (formly Kijiji.cn)&lt;br&gt;mobile: +8613916146826&lt;br&gt;twitter: jianshuo&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='