"http://baixing.com"&gt;baixing.com&lt;/a&gt; (formly Kijiji.cn)&lt;br&gt;mobile: +8613916146826&lt;br&gt;twitter: jianshuo&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-7947842999240195196?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/09/blog-post_30.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-3185276936773441162</guid><pubDate>Tue, 29 Sep 2009 13:53:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-09-29T21:53:27.686+08:00</atom:updated><title>赶爸爸出门了</title><description>小宝从来都是晚上单独和代代躲在书房里喝奶。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;小宝和代代进书房，发现爸爸在书房打电脑，小宝说："爸爸在这里。。。 怎么。。。喝奶？？？？"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;爸爸就被赶了出来。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;过一会儿，小宝推门进卧室："小宝喝完奶了。。。妈妈不拍手。。。为什么？"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;众人赶紧拍手"小宝真能干！"&lt;br&gt; &lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-3185276936773441162?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/09/blog-post_29.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-5629651793167247982</guid><pubDate>Sun, 27 Sep 2009 14:03:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-09-27T22:03:57.796+08:00</atom:updated><title>小宝卖车记</title><description>小宝提了一个小包，里面装满了他的小车。他跑到爸爸这里，说："爸爸，我卖车呢。。。爸爸，我卖车呢"。&lt;br&gt;爸爸说"你有什么车？拿出来给爸爸看一看"。&lt;br&gt;小宝把宝宝打开，给爸爸看。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;爸爸拿了个公交车出来："这个挺好的，多少钱？"&lt;br&gt;小宝："这个轱辘坏了呢。"，然后抢回去，放进自己的包里。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;"这个呢？"爸爸拿了个红车。&lt;br&gt;"这个还没有修呢"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;"这个呢？"爸爸拿了个黄车。&lt;br&gt;"这个是妈妈的"。&lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt;爸爸挑了个很小的车："这个呢？"&lt;br&gt;"这个太。。。小了！"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;"这个呢？"&lt;br&gt;"这个太黄了"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;"这个呢？"爸爸挑了个圆圆的。&lt;br&gt;"这个太圆了"。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;所有的车都调了一个遍，小宝爸爸的手推开，把宝宝拉起来，拎着自己一辆没少的车，高兴地跑到妈妈那里：&lt;br&gt;"妈妈，我卖车呢！妈妈，我卖车呢！"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-5629651793167247982?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/09/blog-post_27.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-4512532553297317802</guid><pubDate>Sat, 26 Sep 2009 11:11:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-09-26T19:11:07.824+08:00</atom:updated><title>你不去打电脑站在这儿干什么？</title><description>小宝遇到楼下的保安叔叔，问道："你不去打电脑，站在这儿。。。干什么？"&lt;br&gt;保安说："我打不动怎么办？"&lt;br&gt;小宝说："你是不是不会呀？我爷爷会，爸爸也会。。。"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-4512532553297317802?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/09/blog-post_26.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-5651280213576196883</guid><pubDate>Fri, 25 Sep 2009 14:01:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-09-25T22:01:11.186+08:00</atom:updated><title>妈妈没回来，闭眼干什么？</title><description>阿姨让小宝睡觉，小宝说："妈妈。。。没回来。。。闭眼。。。干什么！！！"&lt;br&gt; &lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-5651280213576196883?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/09/blog-post_25.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-8832398719659231095</guid><pubDate>Wed, 23 Sep 2009 06:49:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-09-23T14:49:42.986+08:00</atom:updated><title>小宝的car</title><description>小宝的car有&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;代代新car&lt;br&gt;妈妈car&lt;br&gt;妈妈大car - "坐妈妈大car去玩"是小宝的最爱&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-8832398719659231095?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/09/car.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-5194297175881102253</guid><pubDate>Wed, 23 Sep 2009 06:41:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-09-23T14:41:38.054+08:00</atom:updated><title>妈妈亲手制作的小宝照片</title><description>&lt;p class="mobile-photo"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/uploaded_images/banner2-798056-798068.JPG"&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/uploaded_images/banner2-798056-798065.JPG"  border="0" alt="" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;很神气的呢。&lt;br&gt; &lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-5194297175881102253?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/09/blog-post_5063.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-6818124552125674160</guid><pubDate>Wed, 23 Sep 2009 06:22:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-09-23T14:22:04.354+08:00</atom:updated><title>小宝的语言学习期</title><description>小宝现在进入了语言学习的黄金时期，大家说什么，他都学什么。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;他最喜欢的两句话：&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;一句是："我会跳。。。袜子！"说完就乐得满地打滚。其实，我们那一次说的是"华尔兹"不是"袜子"。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;另一句是："我是妈妈的。。。妖怪"。我们明明说是"小乖乖"。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-6818124552125674160?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/09/blog-post_23.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-8481521774821340328</guid><pubDate>Wed, 23 Sep 2009 06:11:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-09-23T14:11:09.889+08:00</atom:updated><title>太好呢！</title><description>- 以后每天给小宝买一辆小红车，好不好？&lt;br&gt;- 太好呢！太好呢！&lt;br&gt; &lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-8481521774821340328?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/09/blog-post.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-5785029150958690125</guid><pubDate>Fri, 11 Sep 2009 16:11:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-09-23T14:15:27.601+08:00</atom:updated><title>小宝受伤了</title><description>小宝的额头摔破了，缝了5针。我的心都碎了。每天想到这件事情，心就缩一下，痛苦得肌肉都能绷紧。 &lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;我真应该在宝宝身上花更多的精力，更多的保护。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-5785029150958690125?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2009/09/blog-post_12.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-5934046550295304934</guid><pubDate>Wed, 27 Aug 2008 08:12:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2008-08-27T16:12:02.904+08:00</atom:updated><title>Google Toolbar Updated</title><description>&lt;a href="http://www.google.com/tools/firefox/toolbar/FT3/intl/en/done_au.html"&gt;Google Toolbar Updated&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-5934046550295304934?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2008/08/google-toolbar-updated.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5609965.post-8205432848601257066</guid><pubDate>Sun, 26 Aug 2007 14:51:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2007-08-26T22:54:02.420+08:00</atom:updated><title></title><description>小宝今天学会两件事情：&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;第一：把大拇指头放进嘴巴里。晚上发现他已经吃的开心异常，阵阵有声。&lt;br /&gt;第二：开始喜欢被人竖着抱起来，靠自己的脖子撑住脑袋，还左看右看的，放下来，他就哭。&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5609965-8205432848601257066?l=www.wangjianshuo.com%2Ffamily%2Findex.htm' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.wangjianshuo.com/family/2007/08/blog-post.htm</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Jian Shuo)</author></item></channel></rss>